flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Get DB Path]
    B --> C[Check schema.sql Exists]
    C -->|Exists| D[Connect to DB]
    C -->|Does Not Exist| E[Print Error & Exit]
    D --> F[Execute Schema]
    F --> G[Seed Initial Data]
    G --> H[Commit Changes]
    H --> I[Print Confirmation]
    I --> J[Fetch & Print Agents]
    J --> K[End]
